                    </div>
                    <div class="problem-sub__title">
                        <big>Here’s what most students say;</big>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="problem-text">
                    <div class="problem-list">
                        <h3><span class="highlight">So much would go wrong if I got a
                                <span class="highlight-brush">poor GPA!</span></span></h3>
                        <ul class="problem-list__items">
                            <li class="problem-list__item">
                                <span class="highlight">Losing</span> all the <span class="highlight">tuition
                                    investment</span>.
                            </li>
                            <li class="problem-list__item">
                                The <span class="highlighd">embarrassment of</span> failing and <span
                                    class="highlight">not graduating</span>.
                            </li>
                            <li class="problem-list__item">
                                Your hopes of getting a job get crushed.
                            </li>
                            <li class="problem-list__item">
                                You could <span class="highlight">jeopardize</span> your <span
                                    class="highlight">financial aid</span>.
                            </li>
                            <li class="problem-list__item">
                                Your dream to apply for scholarship
                                disappears.
                            </li>
                            <li class="problem-list__item">
                                You <span class="highlight">lose</span> a <span class="highlight">chance to
                                    further</span> your <span class="highlight">studies</span>.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="problem-list">
                        <h3><span class="highlight">I didn’t know that <span class="highlight-brush">writing
                                    assignments</span> would be this <span class="highlight-brush">hectic!</span></span>
                        </h3>
                        <ul class="problem-list__items">
                            <li class="problem-list__item">
                                <bold>
                                    <span class="highlight">Especially the research part.</span>
                                </bold>
                                Reading so much, in the hope of finding a piece of useful information.
                            </li>
                            <li class="problem-list__item">
                                <span class="highlight">Assignments</span> come in all sizes, topics, and <span
                                    class="highlight">complexities with limited timeframes</span>. How do you beat
                                such <span class="highlight">deadlines</span>?
                            </li>
                            <li class="problem-list__item">
                                The <bold><span class="highlight">perfectionist professor</span></bold>, who looks
                                for the tiniest mistake to grade you poorly!
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="problem-list">
                        <h3><span class="highlight"><span class="highlight-brush">Balancing school</span>and my life is
                                killing me!</span></h3>
                        <ul class="problem-list__items">
                            <li class="problem-list__item">
