                                down switching between lectures, running to work, and then the day is over. Before I
                                know it, a term paper is staring at me in the eyes, with a very short deadline.”
                                <small>Olga, 28- distance learning student.</small>
                            </li>
                            <li class="problem-list__item">
                                “I never imagined myself <span class="highlight">spending countless hours in the
                                    library</span>, several times every
                                week to complete an assignment, besides, even <span class="highlight">finding the
                                    time</span> to complete assignments
                                <span class="highlight">is hard!</span>”
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
