                                Or
                                • I am a second language learner.
                            </blockquote>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                    <div class="notepaper">
                        <figure class="quote">
                            <blockquote class="curly-quotes">
                                <strong>I can write essays/assignments, but I am too busy/overwhelmed</strong> I am too
                                busy- working jobs, and trying to finance the expensive school life, besides taking care
                                of my family.
                            </blockquote>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                    <div class="notepaper">
                        <figure class="quote">
                            <blockquote class="curly-quotes">
                                <strong>I wish I’d get advice on managing my life in school.</strong>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>
                                        How to get a great paying side-job while in school.
